title: Stocks This Week: Buy Microchip Technology And Facebook
text: The market has historically closed on the upside in November OPEX week since 1985 with most of the strength occurring late in the week.

title: Instagram will test hiding US users' likes
text: Posting on Instagram can come with a rush of validation when likes from friends and strangers come pouring in. But those likes will soon be hidden for some US users.

title: How Facebook stumbled to the edge of a government breakup
text: After a three-year string of scandals, Facebook finds itself staring down four separate antitrust investigations and a front-runner presidential candidate who has made the breakup of the company a key part of her campaign.

title: Better Buy: Facebook vs. Line Corp
text: Should investors steer clear of the troubled social media giant and invest in the growing Japanese company instead?
